title: vb veganburgers
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Polish
description: Vegan burger place minutes from SKM station. Also serves cakes, cookies, green smoothies and juices; during cold season warm soups; during spring and summer fresh salads. Modern and spacious with a children's corner. Offers tea, coffee, yerba mate, and the regional Polish specialty rhubarb lemonade.
